text: My youngest son comes many times in here. So today purposely I want to check on this sport store. It's quite complete the collections and specialized also in badminton which last time my son came by to fix his racket. Reasonable price. We'll drop by again.

Huge variety of badminton equipment, from shoes, rackets, shuttlecock, grip, etc. And on top of that they also have another sport equipment. For each equipment we can get quality equipment from well-known brand like li-ning, yonex, etc.

The service was very fast and professional. Will come again when we need badminton or any sport equipment

Best racket shop in Singapore. Where else can you find a shop owned by a retired World Badminton and US Open Champion in Sg? Run by a veteran couple that knows better for all üëçüèº jokes on those that reviewed saying they are clueless, clearly by ignorant people who thinks they are better than the owners. They usually have long turnover time due to their expertise and meticulous attention to details. Very professional, patient and best in the market.

A specialized store for Badminton sport products. Has many Li-Ning, Yonex equipment. Rackets, shoes, clothing, various support braces from McDavid for hands, legs, racket restring service is available here.

Lady boss is friendly and takes her time to explain on the products. The only feedback is that they dont accept credit cards or ewallets.
I came here to regrip my racket before playing and they helped me regrip it instantly and well. Very satisfied with the service provided here!
